66
00:03:46,805 --> 00:03:47,931
<i>Aku hidup dengan baik.</i>

67
00:03:48,765 --> 00:03:50,266
<i>Tanpa bantuan siapa pun.</i>

68
00:03:52,644 --> 00:03:53,687
<i>Hanya diriku sendiri.</i>

69
00:03:57,983 --> 00:04:01,361
Kau tak bisa bertanggung jawab.
