106
00:06:08,613 --> 00:06:09,781
Paman Muka Seram.

107
00:06:12,116 --> 00:06:13,827
Bisa bawakan makanan kecil kalian?

108
00:06:14,744 --> 00:06:17,288
- Apa?
- Aku beri tahu alasan kalian butuh aku.

109
00:06:18,289 --> 00:06:19,374
Bawakan aku satu.

110
00:06:19,958 --> 00:06:22,502
