224
00:14:46,631 --> 00:14:48,382
Sudah berapa jam kau bekerja di sini?

225
00:14:49,258 --> 00:14:50,134
Kau datang.

226
00:14:51,093 --> 00:14:52,053
Ini hampir selesai.

227
00:14:52,136 --> 00:14:54,764
